[LOW] META-002 validpgpkeys declared but no signature is verified
    validpgpkeys= lists trusted signing key(s) but no source carries a detached signature (.sig/.asc) or a ?signed VCS fragment, so the declared key verifies nothing — signature theatre that can lull a reviewer.
